post.description: Composite beam that resists bending moment by integrally connecting to reinforced concrete slab and steel beam supporting it by shear connector is designed. Depending on the data that  is entered by users, results of deflection checking, shear connector estimation and Heel drop vibration checking as well as design stress checking applied to each part of composite beam and is automatically calculated.
